{"tid":2217557,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"裝修工藏鐵通士巴拿脫罪","createTime":"2020-09-25T13:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T14:21:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"861e6bae53827c3bd53f61ff03d8984ff046ff64","tid":2217557,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/CATCI2WTVRG7BGWPKZ6MMYKHPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FCATCI2WTVRG7BGWPKZ6MMYKHPY%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzqNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=6d7e7e47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FCATCI2WTVRG7BGWPKZ6MMYKHPY%2F&h=4b40517b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/CATCI2WTVRG7BGWPKZ6MMYKHPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n裝修工藏鐵通士巴拿脫罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nDOayXEpQU5bWUHkrzY0pkcw7u8=/2345x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IV4ILU3KDJG6XHR2XOZS4ODVP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnDOayXEpQU5bWUHkrzY0pkcw7u8%3D%2F2345x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIV4ILU3KDJG6XHR2XOZS4ODVP4.jpg&h=3c2cf7c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告吳家豪昨獲聲援人士撐傘護送。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年11月「大三罷」堵路期間，中年裝修工清晨時分將車停泊於吐露港公路，遇警截查，搜出1.5米長鐵通、六角匙及士巴拿等，被控管有攻擊性武器罪。裁判官昨裁定被告脫罪，指涉案工具只是一般工程物品；而雖然附近有堵路，但無法肯定被告管有物品唯一目的是犯案。裁判官並指警員未有警誡便向被告問話，剝奪被告法律權利，做法不妥。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。至於會否向警方索償，吳表示：「睇吓光唔光復到再諗。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官指無警誡問話致不公<br />\n<br />\n裁判官李志豪昨指，搜車警員梁家輝未有警誡被告便問話，被告在未獲告知權利下回答問題，構成不公。而補錄警誡會面口供的警員梁晉榮，則在警誡後才向被告發出羈留人士通知書，「間接剝奪被告法律權利」，做法亦不妥。<br />\n<br />\n李官續指被告管有涉案工具，。。。。。。。。。。，裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n控方欲充公涉案工具，辯方反對。李官指既然罪脫，證物應當歸還被告，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：STCC1098/20"},{"pid":"da3e49053fd73a12796ea053a848284637786478","tid":2217557,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0aee0160ab653adc6954bebb08b5b945794bf4b","tid":2217557,"uid":262406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4tQ8Ok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4tQ8Ok.jpg&h=0eb028ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}